g.text: I believe that solutions led by design thinking have the strength to bring significant changes in communities and organizations. The research insights not only help me with my design projects but also inspire me as a person by inducing empathy. I especially enjoy community design initiatives and co-creation activities, where the designer acts as a moderator of the process.Sunanda SahuUX Design | Heuristic Evaluation | UX research Design Systems | Information Architecture Adobe Suite | Sketch | Figma | Invision
